      "When you are logging in, Surge should be writing to a file called `.netrc`. Would you mind sending me the Surge section of that file so we can see if it’s formatted properly?\n\nIt should be located in `C:\\Users\\Your Name\\.netrc` and look something like this:\n\n```\nmachine surge.sh\n    login kenneth@surge.sh\n    password ab1a1012123abc12345a1ab12345ab12\n```\n\nIf you don’t mind emailing that to me at [kenneth@surge.sh](mailto:kenneth@surge.sh), it would be really helpful. If the file isn’t there, that’s also helpful. Thanks so much for your patience!\n",
